<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">مَرْتَبَتُهُ:</span> <span class="c4">[صَدُوْقٌ]</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَفَاتُهُ:</span> <span class="c2">(٢٥١ هـ)</span>. <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">مَصَادِر تَرْجَمَتِهِ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c1">" الكُنَى وَالأَسْمَاء"</span> <span class="c2">(٣١٣/ ١/ ١٩٩٩)</span>، <span class="c1">"الأَسَامِي وَالكُنَى"</span> <span class="c2">(ل: ٢٧٩/ ب)</span>، <span class="c1">"تَارِيْخ نَيْسَابُوْر"</span> اخْتِصَار الخَلِيْفَة النَّيْسَابُوْرِيُّ <span class="c2">(ص: ٣٣)</span>، <span class="c1">"تَارِيْخ الإِسْلام"</span> <span class="c2">(٦/ ١٩٢)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٩٥]</span> مُحَمَّد بن مُسْلِم بن عُثْمَان بن عَبْد الله، الرَّازِيُّ، ابن وَارَهْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">مَرْوِيَّاتُهُ:</span> رَوَى عَنْهُ فِي <span class="c1">"المُنْتَقَى"</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> حَدِيِثًا وَاحِدًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">حَدِيْثُهُ فِي الكُتُبِ السِّتَّةِ:</span> <span class="c2">(س)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">مَرْتَبَتُهُ:</span> قَالَ الذَّهَبِي: <span class="c1">"الحَافِظُ، الإِمَامُ، المُجَوِّدُ، أَحَدُ الأَعْلامِ"</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ الحَافِظ:</span> <span class="c1">"ثِقَةٌ حَافِظٌ"</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَفَاتُهُ:</span> <span class="c2">(٢٧٠ هـ)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٩٦]</span> مُحَمَّد بن مِهْرَان، النَّيْسَابُوْرِيُّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">مَكَان رِوَايَتِهِ عَنْهُ:</span> <span class="c1">"أَلْقَاب الصَّحَابَة وَالتَّابِعِيْن"</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قَالَ مُحَقّق "الجَامِع لِشُعَب الإِيْمَان" (برقم: ٣٦٨٤): "لَمْ أَعْرِفْهُ".<br>(٢) (برقم: ٨٥١).<br>(٣) "النُّبَلاء" (١٣/ ٢٨).<br>(٤) "التَّقْرِيْب" (برقم: ٦٢٤٢).<br>(٥) (ص: ٧٦).</p> </div>